components.name: Wait for L2 Full Load
components.description: Gates pipeline execution until previous day's L1 to L2 load completes successfully. Checks for 'l1_to_l2_load_successfull' flag with previous business date.

upstream_policy.description: Waits for previous tasks to complete before checking the flag.

connections.purpose: Check L1 to L2 load flag

components.description: Generate unique load identifier for workflow tracking.

components.description: Register workflow session in metadata system and initialize data load tracking.

components.description: Ensure previous day's successful completion before proceeding.

components.name: End
